'From Squeak3.3alpha of 11 January 2002 [latest update: #4726] on 30 January 2002 at 8:53:31 pm'!"Change Set:		includesIdentity-swDate:			30 January 2002Author:			Scott WallaceFixes up one missed reference to References in the module work."!!Object methodsFor: 'viewer' stamp: 'nk 1/30/2002 11:12'!uniqueNameForReferenceOrNil	"If the receiver has a unique name for reference, return it here, else return nil"	| aName |	(References definedNames includesIdentity: self) ifTrue: [^ References definedNames keyAtValue: self].	(aName _ Smalltalk keyAtValue: self ifAbsent: [nil]) ifNotNil: [^ aName].	^ nil! !